      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, it remains in pristine, showroom condition both mechanically and aesthetically. Every detail reflects a legacy of meticulous care, offering the discerning driver an investment-grade experience. We invite you to inspect a vehicle that transcends the standard market, delivering unparalleled quality and sophistication.",
