    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade FD3S Mazda RX-7, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. This example features the legendary 13B-REW twin-rotor engine with its complex sequential turbocharging system functioning flawlessly, providing a linear power band devoid of boost leaks. The chassis maintains its perfect 50/50 weight distribution with pristine double-wishbone suspension and uncompromised bushings. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the apex seals maintain factory-spec compression, and the five-speed longitudinal transmission shifts with short-throw precision into the Torsen limited-slip differential. Every vacuum line, heat shield, and electrical connector is in concours state, free from the typical heat-cycling degradation found in high-mileage examples. A rare opportunity to acquire a pure, unmodified specimen of JDM history.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
