    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or door dings, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and the original factory scent persists. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been strictly garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a full paper trail included. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor\u2014tight, responsive, and quiet.",
      "price": 46500.0,
