    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an impeccable standard. This specimen exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every detail reflects a rigorous commitment to preservation, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade motorcar.",
