    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like royalty. It looks and drives just like it rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no weird smells, just pure perfection. I'm so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love instantly. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014it\u2019s a total dream!",
