    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings and VANOS hub have been addressed as preventative measures. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic handling these chassis are known for. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service binder, the exterior retains its deep luster with no evidence of oxidation or clear coat failure.",
